                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7594" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0170</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1641 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逆势而上，化险为夷：长城汽车供应链双循环构建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Going against the Trend and Avoiding Danger: the Way to Build the Dual-cycle Development Pattern for the&#160;Great&#160;Wall&#160;Motor&#160;Company’s Supply Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏旭光，孙萌，高凌，李向东</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康凯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长城汽车股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长城汽车；供应链风险管理；双循环；供应链结构优化；供应链弹性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The&#160;Great&#160;Wall&#160;Motor&#160;Company; Supply chain risk management;&#160;Dual-cycle development pattern; Supply chain structure optimization; Supply chain resilience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠肺炎疫情持续冲击全球汽车供应链，零部件短缺导致整车厂停工或生产减缓的现象频发。长城汽车面对“断供”危机，逆势而上进行供应链布局优化，逐渐形成需求先行、整车主导、零部件跟随、智能服务推动的国内循环供应链，还形成自研技术及整车工厂全球化、销售渠道多样化的国外动态循环供应链。本案例以全球新冠肺炎疫情引发的供应链中断风险为背景，描述长城汽车识别供应链风险、应对供应链风险并着手修复供应链、面对逆势进行双循环结构优化、突破逆势推进供应链系统弹性提升的过程。通过本案例的学习，可以引导学生思考企业如何进行供应链风险管理以及如何通过供应链结构优化推进供应链弹性提升，深化学生对供应链风险识别与分析、供应链风险管理措施、供应链结构优化、供应链弹性相关理论的学习。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The epidemic of COVID-19 continues to impact the global automotive supply chain. The shortage of parts and components has caused frequent shutdowns or production slowdowns in OEMs. Facing the impact of &quot;supply interruption&quot;, the Great Wall Motor Company has gone against the trend to optimize the layout of the supply chain, gradually forming a domestic circular supply chain driven by demand first, complete vehicles leading, parts following, and intelligent services, and also forming a foreign dynamic circular supply chain with self-developed technology, complete vehicle factory globalization, and diversified sales channels. Taking the risks of supply chain interruption caused by the global COVID-19 as the background, this case describes the process of the Great Wall Motor Company in identifying supply chain risks, responding to supply chain risks and starting to repair the supply chain, optimizing the structure of the dual cycle supply chain in the face of adversity, and breaking through the adversity to promote the elastic improvement of the supply chain system. Through the study of this case, students can be guided to think about how the Great Wall Motor Company can carry out supply chain risk management and how to promote supply chain elasticity through supply chain structure optimization. This will deepen students&#39; understanding of supply chain risk identification and analysis, supply chain risk management measures, supply chain structure optimization, and supply chain resilience.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链风险的识别与分析；供应链风险管理的措施；供应链结构优化；供应链弹性提升</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
